        <h1 class="pt-2">State of device management</h1>
        <p>Not only has technology enabled employees to work through laptops, smartphones, tablets, and other mobile devices, the shift to remote work has increased the need for it. More devices means a greater risk of compromise and organizational security threats, which results in an increased demand for endpoint visibility and monitoring.</p>
        <p>Our respondents told us about their current state of device management: what MDM they use, what devices they’re managing, and what they’re struggling to cover.</p>
