        <h1>MDM deployment and implementation</h1>
        <p>Since our respondents are directly involved in managing their organization’s devices, they can give the greatest insight into why their organization decided to implement an MDM, how long it took to implement, and what some of the challenges were to implementation.</p>
        <div purpose="subsection">
