        <span purpose="section-marker">PART 4</span>
        <h1>Device Management Effectiveness</h1>
        <p>Organizations may have a way to manage devices in their organization, but are they finding their approach to be successful? In this section, our respondents provided insights into how effective their MDM strategy is when it comes to visibility, keeping inventory, incident response, and more.</p>
        <div purpose="subsection">
          <h3>47% have an MDM that provides sufficient visibility into enrolled devices</h3>
          <p>46.8% say their current MDM strategy provides sufficient visibility into their enrolled devices, and collects sufficient security data. 53.2% say it does not.</p>
