          <span purpose="section-marker">PART 5</span>
          <h1>Plans and Priorities for the Future</h1>
          <p>Organizations are only going to see an increase in mobile device usage, especially as they continue remote work into the foreseeable future. But do organizations have MDM strategy at the top of their priority list? Here’s what the future looks like for device management.</p>
